      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. FANATICAL (1) was a big winner in quick time then came home hard into third and beaten 3.5 lengths at Warragul (26.21) last time. Hard to knock his form from this box, unbeaten in two starts. Can measure up this time. SCOUT ACE (2) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 0.8 lengths into second (29.06) at this track in a Grade 5 over 510m. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Leading player again. TRENDY ART (8) turned spotting a big start finishing seventh (26.80) last time in a Grade 4/5 at Warragul. Solid record at the distance winning six races. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from six starts. Can measure up this time. FANTASTIC ZOHAN (6) is worth consideration after filling a hole in a quick run last time.",
